# ⚡ EV Model Popularity & Trend Analysis Dashboard

An **interactive EV adoption analytics dashboard** built with **Streamlit** and **Plotly** — featuring **Year-over-Year growth**, **forecasting**, and **geospatial mapping**.

![Dashboard Preview](images/dashboard_overview.png)

---

## 🚀 Features

- **Smart Filters**: Filter by _State, Make, Model, Model Year_ and select the **Top N models**
- **Visual Exploration**:
  - 📊 Top Makes and Make-Model combinations
  - 🌎 EV registration counts by state (bar chart + U.S. choropleth map)
  - 📈 Year-over-Year growth percentage table
  - 🔮 Forecasting with **Prophet**, with linear regression fallback
  - 🔥 Heatmap: Model × Year (log-scaled)
- **Rich Interactivity**: Fast, responsive visualizations for large datasets
- **CSV Export**: Download data behind all charts, including forecasts and growth metrics

---

## 📂 Dataset

- **Source**: [WA Department of Licensing – Electric Vehicle Population Data](https://data.wa.gov/Transportation/Electric-Vehicle-Population-Data/muir-wid6)
- **Scope**: Battery Electric Vehicles (BEVs) and Plug-in Hybrid EVs registered in Washington State
- **Fields Include**: `Make`, `Model`, `Model Year`, `State`, `County`, etc.

